Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.96,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I have a big gun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:23.69,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I took it from my lord
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.28,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Sick with justice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.17,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I just wanna feel you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.83,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm your angel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.53,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Only a ring away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.31,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You make me violate you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.77,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No matter who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.41,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.95,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No one lives forever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:45.69,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Been burnt in the hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.46,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}By all those pigs out there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:49.11,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's always been hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.77,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}From when I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.31,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}They make me violate them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:53.98,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No matter who they are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.41,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Get down on your knees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.18,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Get a good head on your shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.82,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If it's for your guys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.61,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Go to the end of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.16,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Do what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.92,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Give it with dedication
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.80,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll put out your misery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:29.43,OP-EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Weapon... I have it all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.96,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我有一把威力无比的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:23.69,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这是上天赐予我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.28,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所谓正义让我感到作呕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.17,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我只想感受你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.83,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我是你的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.53,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只是失去了光环
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.31,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}亵渎你 是你自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.77,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管你是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.41,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这里由你做主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.95,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无人可以永生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:45.69,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在地狱里承受灼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.46,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就因为那些围观的鼠辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:49.11,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自我出生以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.77,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一直生活在地狱中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.31,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}亵渎他们 是他们自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:53.98,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管他们是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.41,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给我跪下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.18,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给我放聪明些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.82,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你们还想要小命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.61,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就给我滚到天边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.16,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}放手做你想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.92,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管去全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.80,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我将为你驱逐痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:29.43,OP-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}武器 这就是我的一切
